{"sn47.42:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 47.42 ","sn47.42:0.2":"5. Amatavagga ","sn47.42:0.3":"Samudayasutta ","sn47.42:1.1":"“Catunnam, bhikkhave, satipatthananam samudayanca atthangamanca desessami. ","sn47.42:1.2":"Tam sunatha. ","sn47.42:1.3":"Ko ca, bhikkhave, kayassa samudayo? ","sn47.42:1.4":"Aharasamudaya kayassa samudayo; ","sn47.42:1.5":"aharanirodha kayassa atthangamo. ","sn47.42:1.6":"Phassasamudaya vedananam samudayo; ","sn47.42:1.7":"phassanirodha vedananam atthangamo. ","sn47.42:1.8":"Namarupasamudaya cittassa samudayo; ","sn47.42:1.9":"namarupanirodha cittassa atthangamo. ","sn47.42:1.10":"Manasikarasamudaya dhammanam samudayo; ","sn47.42:1.11":"manasikaranirodha dhammanam atthangamo”ti. ","sn47.42:1.12":"Dutiyam. "}